cs.NI, cs.SE, cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.SY. 

The paper focuses on developing a platform for connected vehicle application development, which involves networking and communication technologies (cs.NI) as well as software engineering (cs.SE) for building, testing, and debugging applications. The platform also emphasizes security (cs.CR) and scalability (cs.DC) to ensure the functional requirements of the applications are met. Finally, the platform is designed for edge-centric cyber-physical systems (cs.SY), which involves the integration of physical and computational components.
